channel.title: Hi, I'm Kemal from Yakamoz Labs
channel.description:
Hi,
I'm Kemal from Belgium, now living in Istanbul.
I've been building iOS apps since 2008 in the evenings/weekends while working full-time as a software engineer at some telecom services company. In 2011 I left my job and started Yakamoz Labs. With the App Store changes decreasing the success rate for indie developers I've pivoted from apps to software components for the iOS platform.
I'm looking forward to sharing and learning from the experiences of other Bootstrapped.fm community members.
